{"tid":1131271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港幾時變左一個要人走佬嘅地方？","createTime":"2019-04-29T14:26:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T10:36:42.000Z","uid":235588,"like":60,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1d577457369acfd83e573cd0851b1f7413dec75e","tid":1131271,"uid":235588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T14:26:05.000Z","msg":"呢幾年香港即使樓價再高，生活壓力再大，政治前途幾絕望都好，香港起碼有一片瓦遮頭，有小小容身之地。但係依加已經淪落為一個，大難臨頭要各自飛嘅地獄。睇住林榮基因為驚引渡條例比人帶返去大陸受審而走佬台灣，好多人都屌佢之前講一套做一套。不過問心嗰句，如果你係佢，你其實冇得揀，命仔緊要過一切。我地要問嘅係：當香港法制唔能夠再比到香港人信心，當條法例會令到香港人擔心自己成為中共嘅眼中釘，比大陸以莫須有罪名名正言順拉你返去，香港係咪連最後嘅人生自由都無？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次引渡條約係可怕過23條，威脅緊你同我嘅人身安全，所以如果未跟進過相關爭議嘅你哋，麻煩睇吓而家香港發生咩事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔該你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fe4dad219bb327bba1870d1e391ddbac6605d8","tid":1131271,"uid":146215,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T14:27:43.000Z","msg":"自1997年7月1日起"},{"pid":"81f3bf4b1cb38148bf7a51253d9a6ad2a5cce8db","tid":1131271,"uid":63909,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"f6fe4dad219bb327bba1870d1e391ddbac6605d8","tid":1131271,"uid":146215,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T14:27:43.000Z","msg":"自1997年7月1日起"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T14:29:15.000Z","msg":"係鐵娘子係鄰近地區仆親個時"},{"pid":"36f26711aaa8b77ecf0dca704bea8051dcf3b16a","tid":1131271,"uid":209487,"like":1,"dislike":39,"score":-38,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T14:29:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7f7b4b2312715f0797c04d0e56a05af5a15c813","tid":1131271,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T14:37:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"